rewards
Step 1: As part of our commitment to creating an engaging and rewarding experience for our users, we are excited to announce that you can now earn daily rewards just by visiting our site! That's right, log in once a day and claim your reward from the reward panel.
Step 2: To qualify for daily rewards, make sure you are registered with us and log in to your account every day. Once logged in, you will see a reward panel where you can claim your daily reward. These rewards will include R-VR tokens, entry to reward pools.
Step 3: Don't miss your chance to win daily rewards and join the Reality VR community even more. Log in to your account and claim your reward every day to keep the rewards coming! Thank you for being a part of our project and we look forward to continue rewarding our users for their participation and engagement.
